{"id":"hadarezer","term":"Hadarezer","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Adod is his help, the name given to Hadadezer (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 8:3\">2 Sam. 8:3-12</a>) in <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 10\">2 Sam. 10</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Samuel 8:3","2 Samuel 10"]}